  "id": "BIT-tomcat-2026-34500",
  "summary": "Apache Tomcat: OCSP checks sometimes soft-fail with FFM even when soft-fail is disabled",
  "details": "CLIENT_CERT authentication does not fail as expected for some scenarios when soft fail is disabled and FFM is used in Apache Tomcat.\n\nThis issue affects Apache Tomcat: from 11.0.0 through 11.0.20, from 10.1.22 through 10.1.53, from 9.0.92 through 9.0.116.\n\nUsers are recommended to upgrade to version 11.0.21, 10.1.54 or 9.0.117, which fixes the issue.",
